Howard W. Smith III
Executive Compensation
As President at WALKER & DUNLOP INC, Howard W. Smith III made $2,623,977 in total compensation.  Of this total $500,000 was received as a salary, $1,000,000 was received as a bonus, $400,004 was received in stock options, $714,973 was awarded as stock and $9,000 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


